------------------------------------------------

This directory contains examples demonstrating

[1] traversing the AST using AstSimpleProcessing

[2] computing attributes using 
    [2a] AstTopDownProcessing, 
    [2b] AstBottomUpProcessing,
    [2c] AstTopDownBottomUpProcessing

[3] using member variables in AstProcessing classes for computing
    accumulated results (accumulators).

[4] generating a pdf file containing the information of the AST.

[5] generating a dot file (and postscript) for visualizing the AST
    as a graph.

[6] adding user-defined information to 
    [6a] pdf output
    [6b] dot output

[7] Using class AstAttribute to 
    [7a] attach information to the AST.
    [7b] add values of AST node attributes in a pdf output

[8] accessing basic information at AST nodes.

------------------------------------------------

Brief overview of examples:

* printVar: demonstrates [1],[3],[5],[8]
* loopInfo: demonstrates [2c],[3],[4],[5],[7a,7b].

For more information see the README file in each
directory and the documented files.

------------------------------------------------

Not demonstrated yet: [2a],[2b],[6]

------------------------------------------------
